			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_000961_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>57 Sloane St</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">9<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> Feb<hi rend="sup">y</hi></p>
<lb/><p>My Dear Sir </p>
<lb/><p><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">rs</hi> L.</persName> and 
<lb/>I have much 
<lb/>pleasure in 
<lb/>accepting your 
<lb/>kind invitation 
<lb/>for Monday 
<lb/>the 16<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> and 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_000961_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>it will give us 
<lb/>great pleasure 
<lb/>to meet your 
<lb/>worthy rector<reg>.</reg>
<lb/>Should anything 
<lb/>turn up to make 
<lb/>that day 
<w>incon-<lb break="no"/>venient</w> a note 
<lb/>will delay us 
<lb/>without any 
<lb/>inconvenience 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_000961_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'--> 
<lb/>till the 19<hi rend="sup">th</hi> as we 
<lb/>have no 
<w>engage-<lb break="no"/>ment</w> for that 
<lb/>day. </p>
<lb/><p>David Livingston </p>
			
</div>
